<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: PvP &amp; Rogues</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Ragok">Ragok</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 9:45 a.m. 22/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: PvP &amp; Rogues<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1127" TARGET=_self>PvP &amp; Rogues</A> (Depravity)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>From grouping with a rouge throughout p3 i can tell you that "assassination" (in its true meaning) is impossible. There is no instant kill. Even a successfull backstab will not even be close to killing another in one shot (if he is full hp). On the other hand, sneak and hide do come in handy, and are a very good asset in PvP. Depending on what poisons they imp for rouges, this will decide how much of a quick strike character it will be. As it is right now they are underpowered fighters with some special abilities.

<P>Mind you, they are still being tweaked (as are most of the classes), so don't let this decide it for you if you realy want to play one.
<P>Ragok Arnskull
<BR>skull@lvdi.net
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
